onthly_payouts.png 750w,\n/static/0a3148696147818e89e3290a39b8659f/00d43/april_2020_monthly_payouts.png 1000w,\n/static/0a3148696147818e89e3290a39b8659f/236d7/april_2020_monthly_payouts.png 1486w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"revamped-invitation-preferences\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#revamped-invitation-preferences\" aria-label=\"revamped invitation preferences permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Revamped Invitation Preferences</h3>\n<p>We've revamped the <a href=\"/hackers/invitations.html#invitation-preferences\">Invitation Preferences</a> page with more options to specify and control your invitation settings. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"invitation preferences\"\n        title=\"invitation preferences\"\n        src=\"/static/1f3332eee6e5f674dc67e95c5b8f065e/0b533/april_2020_invitation_preferences.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1f3332eee6e5f674dc67e95c5b8f065e/fac75/april_2020_invitation_preferences.png 125w,\n/static/1f3332eee6e5f674dc67e95c5b8f065e/63868/april_2020_invitation_preferences.png 250w,\n/static/1f3332eee6e5f674dc67e95c5b8f065e/0b533/april_2020_invitation_preferences.png 500w,\n/static/1f3332eee6e5f674dc67e95c5b8f065e/1d69c/april_2020_invitation_preferences.png 750w,\n/static/1f3332eee6e5f674dc67e95c5b8f065e/00d43/april_2020_invitation_preferences.png 1000w,\n/static/1f3332eee6e5f674dc67e95c5b8f065e/3ceac/april_2020_invitation_preferences.png 1456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hacker-following\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hacker-following\" aria-label=\"hacker following permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hacker Following</h3>\n<p>In order to keep up-to-date with your favorite hackers, we introduce the new <a href=\"/hackers/following.html\">Hacker Following</a> feature. This enables you to keep track of your favorite hackers and to quickly see their activity on HackerOne.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 138.39999999999998%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker following\"\n        title=\"hacker following\"\n        src=\"/static/45c060443be53e60b98aa86201377bb3/e17e5/april_2020_following.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/45c060443be53e60b98aa86201377bb3/fac75/april_2020_following.png 125w,\n/static/45c060443be53e60b98aa86201377bb3/63868/april_2020_following.png 250w,\n/static/45c060443be53e60b98aa86201377bb3/e17e5/april_2020_following.png 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>You can filter the activity of the hackers you're following with our new <strong>Hackers I am following</strong> filter on the Hacktivity page.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 306px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hacker following filter\"\n        title=\"hacker following filter\"\n        src=\"/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/98b92/april_2020_hacker_following_filter.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/fac75/april_2020_hacker_following_filter.png 125w,\n/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/63868/april_2020_hacker_following_filter.png 250w,\n/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/98b92/april_2020_hacker_following_filter.png 306w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We also introduce the Followed Hackers page on the Hacker Dashboard to help you manage the hackers you're following.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"followed hackers\"\n        title=\"followed hackers\"\n        src=\"/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/0b533/april_2020_followed_hackers.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/fac75/april_2020_followed_hackers.png 125w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/63868/april_2020_followed_hackers.png 250w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/0b533/april_2020_followed_hackers.png 500w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/1d69c/april_2020_followed_hackers.png 750w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/00d43/april_2020_followed_hackers.png 1000w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/93ba6/april_2020_followed_hackers.png 2874w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/changelog/2020/april","title":"April 2020"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}